org.fife.rsta.ui.search

Interface SearchListener

  • All Superinterfaces:
    java.util.EventListener
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    MainFrame, RSTAUIDemoApp

    public interface SearchListener
extends java.util.EventListener
    Listens for events fired from a Find or Replace dialog/tool bar. Applications can implement this class to listen for the user searching for text, and actually perform the operation via SearchEngine in response.
    Version:
    1.0
    Author:
    Robert Futrell
